svg.text: Source:World Intellectual Property OrganizationGlobal Innovation Index 2007-2017

Switzerland, home of ETH Zurich, and an ecosystem of innovators, ranks #1 in 2017. Robotics and Biotechnology innovation continue to drive the research institutes of ETH Zurich and The University of Zurich.
